TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1816","checkdouble":"192351"},{"date":"23:20 30/07","title":"V\u00ec sao Paul Pogba kh\u00f4ng thay ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/vi-sao-paul-pogba-khong-thay-kieu-toc-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thomas Tuchel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Edinson Cavani, c\u1ef1u HLV Dortmund kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cavani \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real quan t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf cho Ronaldo, khi m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 Neymar, Mbappe hay Eden Hazard g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3, Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Edinson Cavani.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thomas Tuchel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Edinson Cavani h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thomas Tuchel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Edinson Cavani h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/5/Thomas-Tuchel-phat-bieu-ve-Edinson-Cavani-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cavani \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Lopetegui \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Cavani, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Bernabeu. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong l\u1eabn ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c PSG b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987, Real Madrid ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Theo Don Balon, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/psg-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-real-vu-edinson-cavani-180-192189.html\" target=\"_blank\">PSG s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Cavani</span> cho Los Blancos. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ef1u sao Napoli n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNeymar c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Cavani, si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n Cavani r\u1eddi s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n thu v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi, Morata v\u00e0 Higuain l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c PSG nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Dortmund mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Cavani</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thomas Tuchel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Edinson Cavani, c\u1ef1u HLV Dortmund kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cavani ghi ban tu da phat de giai cuu PSG\" title=\"Cavani ghi b\u00e0n t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u PSG\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/23/psg-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-real-vu-edinson-cavani.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Tuchel mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Cavani \u1edf l\u1ea1i PSG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nghe th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c Real Madrid quan t\u00e2m Cavani, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho l\u1eafm. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, Cavani kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec c\u1ea3. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf PSG v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCavani l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a PSG, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u1eb1m trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra \u0111i. PSG s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb d\u00e0nh cho Cavani, \u01b0u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 gi\u1eef c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPSG m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Buffon theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao m\u1edbi. PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1815","checkdouble":"192352"},{"date":"00:32 31/07","title":"Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 Jurgen Klopp: Ai chi ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/jose-mourinho-va-jurgen-klopp-ai-chi-tien-chuyen-nhuong-nhieu-hon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Khi so s\u00e1nh v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ea1o chi tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1eefa Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 Jurgen Klopp, nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng hai chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia n\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ch\u00edn, m\u1ed9t m\u01b0\u1eddi.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ai chi nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n h\u01a1n?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu x\u00e9t t\u1eeb c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c th\u00e1ng 5/2016 khi Jose Mourinho b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Man Utd, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n hai chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia \u0111\u1ed5 v\u00e0o th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch nhau l\u00e0 bao. Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng 411.55* tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn trong n\u0103m d\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1ecbch 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jose Mourinho va Jurgen Klopp deu chi rat nhieu tien tren thi truong chuyen nhuong.\" title=\"Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u1ec1u chi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/jose-mourinho-va-jurgen-klopp-ai-chi-tien-chuyen-nhuong-nhieu-hon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u1ec1u chi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018, Klopp th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y Liverpool chi 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Virgil Van Dijk. H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, The Klopp b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam b\u1ed1n g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t g\u1ed3m Alisson Becker (67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng), Naby Keita (53.75), Fabinho (43) v\u00e0 Xherdan Shaqiri (13.5).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Jose Mourinho trong hai n\u0103m qua c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ti\u00eau t\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a Man Utd s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 392.55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n Man Utd chi ra tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda Liverpool v\u1edbi ba b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng Fred (53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng), Diogo Dalot (19) v\u00e0 Lee Grant (1.5).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ai hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t danh hi\u1ec7u, Jose Mourinho \u0111ang nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n khi \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 3 chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch cho Man Utd. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 Carabao Cup 2016-17, Europa League 2016-17 v\u00e0 FA Community Shield 2016. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Jurgen Klopp ba l\u1ea7n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 nh\u00ec, ch\u01b0a gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 l\u00e3i tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Jurgen Klopp l\u1ea1i nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n. Liverpool thu v\u1ec1 289.65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong hai n\u0103m qua, ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 The Kop ch\u1ec9 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 chi ra 121.9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Mourinho ch\u1ec9 thu v\u1ec1 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 85.3 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf Man Utd ph\u1ea3i b\u00f9 th\u00eam ra l\u1edbn g\u1ea5p r\u01b0\u1ee1i Liverpool v\u1edbi con s\u1ed1 307.25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>* S\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u t\u1eeb Sky Sports.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Mourinho v\u00e0 Klopp:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jose-mourinho-co-nguy-co-bi-sa-thai-cao-nhat-tai-premier-league-172-192349.html\">Jose Mourinho c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i cao nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-toi-307-jose-mourinho-cau-cuu-nhom-tru-cot-man-utd-184-192346.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 30/7: Jose Mourinho c\u1ea7u c\u1ee9u nh\u00f3m tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Man Utd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/4-dieu-mourinho-can-lam-de-cuu-van-tour-du-dau-tham-hoa-cua-mu-172-192341.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u Mourinho c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 MU kh\u00f4ng r\u01a1i v\u00e0o th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 2018/19</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nho-joe-gomez-jurgen-klopp-khong-mua-them-hau-ve-172-192350.html\">Nh\u1edd Joe Gomez, Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huy-diet-mu-klopp-danh-loi-ca-ngoi-cho-1-cai-ten-172-192240.html\">H\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t M.U, Klopp d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i cho 1 c\u00e1i t\u00ean</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-dat-nhat-the-gioi-klopp-van-khen-re-172-192219.html\">Alisson \u0111\u1eaft nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Klopp v\u1eabn khen... r\u1ebb</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1814","checkdouble":"192353"},{"date":"06:17 31/07","title":"Cesar Azpilicueta n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 HLV Sarri?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/cesar-azpilicueta-noi-gi-ve-hlv-sarri.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Cesar Azpilicueta ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Maurizio Sarri, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Azpilicueta \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao HLV Sarri</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/chinh-thuc-chelsea-sa-thai-hlv-antonio-conte-465-191114.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i HLV Conte</span> v\u00e0 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Maurizio Sarri. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111ang t\u00edch c\u1ef1c c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cesar Azpilicueta ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Maurizio Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cesar Azpilicueta ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Maurizio Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/cesar-azpilicueta-noi-gi-ve-hlv-sarri.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Azpilicueta \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao HLV Sarri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCesar Azpilicueta ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Maurizio Sarri, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV m\u1edbi, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u tri\u1ebft l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t l\u00ean\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cChelsea kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, b\u1edfi v\u1eady ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. Nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u00edch nghi t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV m\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u00e0o Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Chelsea s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Man City, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Azpilicueta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Sarri th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 khi c\u00f2n d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Napoli, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u00f4ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt n\u00e0y \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Azpilicueta noi ve tran dau Barca vs Chelsea\" title=\"Azpilicueta n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barca vs Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/16/Azpilicueta-phat-bieu-ve-tinh-canh-bi-dat-cua-Chelsea-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Azpilicueta s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Cesar Azpilicueta th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 trong h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Conte, m\u00f9a t\u1edbi r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o th\u00ec anh c\u0169ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o mi\u1ec5n l\u00e0 HLV c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ed1t cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1813","checkdouble":"192354"},{"date":"06:44 31/07","title":"HLV PSG l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 tin \u0111\u1ed3n Cavani s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/28/hlv-psg-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-edinson-cavani.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thomas Tuchel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Edinson Cavani, c\u1ef1u HLV Dortmund kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cavani \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real quan t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf cho Ronaldo, khi m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 Neymar, Mbappe hay Eden Hazard g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3, Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Edinson Cavani.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thomas Tuchel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Edinson Cavani h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thomas Tuchel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Edinson Cavani h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/5/Thomas-Tuchel-phat-bieu-ve-Edinson-Cavani-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cavani \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Lopetegui \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Cavani, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Bernabeu. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong l\u1eabn ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c PSG b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987, Real Madrid ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Theo Don Balon, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/psg-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-real-vu-edinson-cavani-180-192189.html\" target=\"_blank\">PSG s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Cavani</span> cho Los Blancos. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ef1u sao Napoli n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNeymar c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Cavani, si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n Cavani r\u1eddi s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n thu v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi, Morata v\u00e0 Higuain l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c PSG nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Dortmund mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Cavani</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thomas Tuchel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Edinson Cavani, c\u1ef1u HLV Dortmund kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cavani ghi ban tu da phat de giai cuu PSG\" title=\"Cavani ghi b\u00e0n t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u PSG\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/23/psg-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-real-vu-edinson-cavani.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Tuchel mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Cavani \u1edf l\u1ea1i PSG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nghe th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c Real Madrid quan t\u00e2m Cavani, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho l\u1eafm. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, Cavani kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec c\u1ea3. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf PSG v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCavani l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a PSG, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u1eb1m trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra \u0111i. PSG s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb d\u00e0nh cho Cavani, \u01b0u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 gi\u1eef c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPSG m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Buffon theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao m\u1edbi. PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1812","checkdouble":"192355"},{"date":"06:18 31/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 31/7: Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ec1u l\u00f2ng b\u1eb1ng 2 bom t\u1ea5n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-317-mourinho-duoc-chieu-long-bang-2-bom-tan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 31/7.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ec1u l\u00f2ng b\u1eb1ng 2 bom t\u1ea5n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb t\u1edd Guardian, M.U chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb khi\u1ebfn Jose Mourinho vui l\u00f2ng khi ch\u1ed1t 2 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Perisic v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 Harry Maguire, 2 ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb h\u01a1n 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 c\u1ea3 2 trong \u00edt ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi, khi phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n h\u01a1n 1 tu\u1ea7n n\u1eefa l\u00e0 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i (h\u1ea1n ch\u00f3t 9/8).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 31/7 MU chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00edch n\u1ed5 2 bom t\u1ea5n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 317 MU chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00edch n\u1ed5 2 bom t\u1ea5n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-317-MU-chuan-bi-kich-no-2-bom-tan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 31/7: M.U chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00edch n\u1ed5 2 bom t\u1ea5n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nReal Madrid chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Courtois<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau duy nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 Los Blancos nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn \u1edf Chelsea m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y &ndash; trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Eden Hazard \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Real c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ecf ra h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi Willian, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 Man United l\u1eabn Barca nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea nh\u1eafm bom t\u1ea5n Lewandowski<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c The Blues quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y, khi anh th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chia tay Bayern Munich. M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 Chelsea h\u1ecfi mua Lewandowski r\u01a1i v\u00e0o 100 tri\u1ec7u euro c\u00f9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y HLV Niko Kovac \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Lewandowski b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M.U nh\u1eadn th\u00eam t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong c\u01a1n b\u00e3o ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1ea5t th\u00eam 3 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, b\u1ed9 ba Ander Herrera, Eric Bailly v\u00e0 Chris Smalling \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Real Madrid, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ra s\u00e2n \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 31/7\" title=\"Herrera\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/sao-mu-lo-so-bi-cac-tai-nang-tre-dan-em-cuop-cho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 31/7: Th\u00eam Herrera d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Everton nh\u1eafm sao th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng M.U<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, nh\u01b0ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Marcos Rojo \u0111ang b\u1ea5p b\u00eanh nh\u1ea5t trong nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Everton \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho ng\u00f4i sao Argentina, khi s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi ra 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Everton c\u0169ng l\u00e0 CLB \u0111ang c\u1ea1nh tranh trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh M.U.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1811","checkdouble":"192358"},{"date":"06:34 31/07","title":"BTC ICC t\u1ecf ra th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi Mourinho v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/btc-icc-to-ra-thong-cam-voi-mourinho-ve-luc-luong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu ICC Charlie Stillitano \u2013 HLV Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 d\u00f9 M.U tr\u1ea3i qua v\u00f4 v\u00e0n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1eeb giai \u0111o\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00eanh v\u1ef1c<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Liverpool h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-1, trong \u0111\u00f3 Mourinho th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 r\u1eb1ng, l\u00fac n\u00e0y M.U kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, khi h\u1ecd thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t v\u00ec nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do kh\u00e1c nhau.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed3ng c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf ICC &ndash; \u00f4ng Charlie Stillitano cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y. Jose Mourinho mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 cam k\u1ebft b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf tour du \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eb1ng, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1n gi\u00e1, ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i (ICC), v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean c\u1ea3 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u00f4ng \u1ea5y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u00d4ng \u1ea5y ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eed th\u00e1ch trong m\u1ed9t n\u0103m World Cup, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y c\u00f2n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n v\u00ec Premier League di\u1ec5n ra s\u1edbm. \u0110\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn d\u00e0nh cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, Mourinho \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 n\u00f3i l\u00ean quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 b\u1edfi BTC gi\u1ea3i ICC\" title=\"Jose Mourinho tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u1ecb nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t gh\u1ebf cao nh\u1ea5t.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/diem-tin-toi-307-jose-mourinho-cau-cuu-nhom-tru-cot-man-utd.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 b\u1edfi BTC gi\u1ea3i ICC</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang xem x\u00e9t thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ecbch tr\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0o n\u0103m t\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ee9, nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 sao n\u0103m sau kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i World Cup n\u00ean m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd vui m\u1eebng v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2019, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec nh\u01b0 n\u0103m nay.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;C\u00f3 l\u1ebd, t\u00f4i l\u00e0 Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a CLB h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Mourinho, d\u00f9 l\u00fac n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y. T\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Mourinho. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh (Liverpool), trong m\u1ed9t SV\u0110 c\u00f3 100 ngh\u00ecn C\u0110V. Mourinho l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a gi\u1ea3i ICC l\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y, m\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c HLV tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t vui l\u00f2ng khi s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng&rdquo; &ndash; Charlie Stillitano k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 b\u1edfi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u ICC, nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u00f4ng c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 cam k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a BL\u0110 tr\u00ean phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jose-mourinho-va-jurgen-klopp-ai-chi-tien-chuyen-nhuong-nhieu-hon-172-192353.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/jose-mourinho-va-jurgen-klopp-ai-chi-tien-chuyen-nhuong-nhieu-hon.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jose-mourinho-va-jurgen-klopp-ai-chi-tien-chuyen-nhuong-nhieu-hon-172-192353.html\">Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 Jurgen Klopp: Ai chi ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n?</span><br>\r\nKhi so s\u00e1nh v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ea1o chi tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1eefa Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 Jurgen Klopp, nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng hai chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia n\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ch\u00edn, m\u1ed9t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-khung-hoang-tien-mua-giai-khi-van-de-khong-chi-la-luc-luong-172-192337.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/mu-khung-hoang-tien-mua-giai-khi-van-de-khong-chi-la-luc-luong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-khung-hoang-tien-mua-giai-khi-van-de-khong-chi-la-luc-luong-172-192337.html\">M.U kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i: Khi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\n4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu, 0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng (t\u00ednh trong 90 ph\u00fat) &ndash; \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, ch\u00ednh Mourinho khi\u1ebfn M.U g\u1eb7p kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1810","checkdouble":"192359"},{"date":"06:50 31/07","title":"S\u1ebfp l\u1edbn Napoli ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Ronaldo l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/sep-lon-napoli-chi-trich-ronaldo-la-hop-dong-thuong-mai.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai c\u0169ng th\u00edch th\u00fa khi CR7 chuy\u1ec3n sang Serie A. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Napoli ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Juventus v\u00ec chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo qu\u00e1 hoang ph\u00ed.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nRonaldo sang Juve, Napoli k\u00e9m vui<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp danh hi\u1ec7u Serie A trong v\u00e0i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Napoli ch\u1eb3ng \u01b0a g\u00ec Juventus. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng m\u1ea5y vui v\u1ebb, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n e ng\u1ea1i khi B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0 th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111em v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi Cristiano Ronaldo. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Napoli \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng Aurelio De Laurentiis cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Cristiano \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t cho Juventus. \u0110\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, vi\u1ec7c chi tr\u1ea3 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng qu\u00e1 cao cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nguy hi\u1ec3m. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Napoli ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Juventus v\u00ec chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo\" title=\"cristiano ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/sep-lon-napoli-chi-trich-ronaldo-la-hop-dong-thuong-mai.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Napoli ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Juventus v\u00ec chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;M\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cristiano ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p l\u00fd v\u1edbi quy m\u00f4 c\u1ee7a Juventus. <strong>T\u00f4i t\u1ef1 h\u1ecfi li\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 kh\u00f4n ngoan c\u1ee7a Juve, hay \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i.</strong> N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n tr\u1ea3 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3, s\u1edbm hay mu\u1ed9n, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i b\u1ea1n&rdquo; &ndash; Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Napoli t\u1ecf ra nghi ng\u1edd.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi chuy\u1ec3n sang \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 115 tri\u1ec7u euro, CR7 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 30 tri\u1ec7u euo/m\u00f9a, t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang nh\u1eadn t\u1ea1i Real Madrid nh\u01b0ng l\u00e0 phi l\u00fd \u1edf Juventus. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 4 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Napoli ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Juventus v\u00ec chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Jorge Mendes. Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch De Laurentiis ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;Mendes n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng Ronaldo s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0103n n\u00ean l\u00e0m ra.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;V\u00ec v\u1eady, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb anh \u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng 250 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00e0 Cristiano ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Napoli, v\u00e0 100 tri\u1ec7u euro ti\u1ebfp theo s\u1ebd d\u00e0nh cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. B\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00f3, CR7 s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 tr\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n cho ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh. Sau \u0111\u00f3, Juve xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00e1 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-den-juventus-gia-ve-serie-a-tang-600-176-192347.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/cristiano-ronaldo-den-juventus-gia-ve-serie-a-tang-600.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-den-juventus-gia-ve-serie-a-tang-600-176-192347.html\">Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus: Gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 Serie A t\u0103ng 600%</span><br>\r\nGi\u00e1 v\u00e9 Serie A c\u00f3 n\u01a1i t\u0103ng g\u1ea5p 6 l\u1ea7n so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0103n theo c\u01a1n s\u1ed1t Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-tro-lai-juventus-tap-luyen-cung-dong-doi-176-192282.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/ronaldo-tro-lai-juventus-tap-luyen-cung-dong-doi.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-tro-lai-juventus-tap-luyen-cung-dong-doi-176-192282.html\">Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i</span><br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110TQG v\u00e0 gi\u1edd m\u1edbi chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e2n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1809","checkdouble":"192360"},{"date":"06:56 31/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (31/7/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/31/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-3172018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>