\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">AEK Athens (Hy L\u1ea1p) - Galatasaray (TNK)</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1808","checkdouble":"192362"},{"date":"15:19 30/07","title":"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, HLV Park Hang Seo \u2018c\u1ea5m c\u1eeda\u2019 b\u00e1o ch\u00ed","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/olympic-viet-nam-dinh-trong-tro-lai-hlv-park-hang-seo-cam-cua-bao-chi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp s\u00e1ng 30/7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng dai d\u1eb3ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1i CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.</h2><h2>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u1edf bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 30/7, trung v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t n\u00e0y ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o khi\u1ebfn HLV Park Hang Seo b\u1edbt lo h\u01a1n b\u1edfi \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea5m c\u1eeda h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea5m c\u1eeda h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/20180729-olympic-viet-nam-nhan-tin-vui-tu-dinh-trong-1.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau h\u01a1n 1 th\u00e1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp v\u1edbi gi\u00e1o \u00e1n ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a b\u00e1c s\u1ef9 Choi Joo Young. B\u00e1c s\u0129 Choi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb cho Park Ji Sung v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tu\u1ea5n Anh. \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng b\u1ecb tr\u00e0n d\u1ecbch v\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00f9ng c\u1ed5 ch\u00e2n n\u00ean trung v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian 1 th\u00e1ng r\u01b0\u1ee1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, ch\u00ednh HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp m\u1edbi b\u00e1c s\u0129 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c Choi Ju Young sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1eefa tr\u1ecb cho c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cNh\u01b0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y, h\u00f4m nay \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i sau th\u1eddi gian tr\u1ecb li\u1ec7u c\u00f9ng b\u00e1c s\u1ef9 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. B\u00e1c s\u1ef9 Choi Joo Young l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i n\u00ean t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edbi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c nhanh h\u01a1n\u201d, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay\u00a030/7, HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 cho ph\u00e9p gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ghi h\u00ecnh kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng trong kho\u1ea3ng 30 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. Sau \u0111\u00f3, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u1eed tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e1y \u1ea3nh, m\u00e1y ghi h\u00ecnh n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p t\u00e1c nghi\u1ec7p khi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn cho th\u1ea7y Park cho th\u1ea5y d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u00f4ng \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef b\u00ed m\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-cho-hong-duy-lo-tieu-chi-chon-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam-168-192311.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-cho-hong-duy-lo-tieu-chi-chon-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-cho-hong-duy-lo-tieu-chi-chon-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam-168-192311.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebfc cho H\u1ed3ng Duy, l\u1ed9 ti\u00eau ch\u00ed ch\u1ecdn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br />\r\nTrao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 H\u1ed3ng Duy, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u00f4ng c\u0169ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng ti\u00eau ch\u00ed tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-ham-mo-co-the-khong-duoc-xem-olympic-viet-nam-thi-dau-o-asiad-168-192307.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/27/nguoi-ham-mo-co-the-khong-duoc-xem-olympic-viet-nam-thi-dau-o-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-ham-mo-co-the-khong-duoc-xem-olympic-viet-nam-thi-dau-o-asiad-168-192307.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ASIAD</span><br />\r\nM\u1ee9c ph\u00ed b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh qu\u00e1 cao l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ASIAD.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1807","checkdouble":"192323"},{"date":"15:22 30/07","title":"Sao x\u1eb9t l\u1ea1c quan v\u1edbi kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/31/sao-xet-lac-quan-voi-khoi-dau-moi-tai-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Emerson Palmieri h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00ed th\u1ebf d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng, Chelsea b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u00e2n binh t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm Emerson Palmieri t\u1eeb AS Roma v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 17,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c g\u00ec trong n\u1eeda n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Stamford Bridge.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Emerson c\u1ee7a Chelsea t\u1ef1 tin h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Emerson c\u1ee7a Chelsea t\u1ef1 tin h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/31/Hau-ve-Emerson-Palmieri-da-san-sang-tro-lai-thi-dau-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Emerson c\u1ee7a Chelsea t\u1ef1 tin h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi c\u00f9ng t\u00e2n HLV Sarri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec v\u1eady m\u00e0 Emerson c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y thi\u1ebfu t\u1ef1 tin m\u00e0 tr\u00e1i l\u1ea1i, anh l\u1ea1c quan v\u00e0 kh\u00ed th\u1ebf h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i: \u201cQuan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u00f4i v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean m\u1edbi.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, t\u00f4i gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng M\u1ed9t t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00f4i qua n\u1eeda ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, ch\u00ednh th\u1ebf m\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0 th\u00edch nghi c\u0169ng ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1c, t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n sung m\u00e3n c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t, phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cSarri ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111ang th\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t lu\u1ed3ng gi\u00f3 m\u1edbi v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Napoli c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u1edf Serie A v\u00e0 \u00fd th\u1ee9c r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia t\u00e0i n\u0103ng ra sao. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u0129nh h\u1ed9i tri\u1ebft l\u00fd v\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Sarri, \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c ban \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u1ec9 sau m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chelsea c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i hai tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1eb7p Arsenal v\u00e0 Lyon, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh v\u1edbi Man City.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-chuong-su-moi-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang-172-187380.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-thu-thach-long-kien-nhan-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-chuong-su-moi-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang-172-187380.html\">Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri: Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1eed m\u1edbi v\u1edbi g\u00e3 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng</span><br>\r\nChelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri thay th\u1ebf HLV Conte trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao v\u00e0 qua \u0111\u00e2y, Stamford Bridge s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i, k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1806","checkdouble":"192324"},{"date":"15:39 30/07","title":"V\u00e9 xem \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng: VFF \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 4.0","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/ve-xem-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-giai-tu-hung-vff-ap-dung-cong-nghe-40.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u00e1c t\u1edd b\u00e1o t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ousmane Dembele \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\">\r\n            <h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Barca ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Dembele</h2>\r\n            <img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Barca ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Dembele h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Barca ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Dembele h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Giam-doc-the-thao-Barca-chot-tuong-lai-Dembele-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ousmane Dembele \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u1ea1i Camp Nou\u00a0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, t\u1edd Mundo Deportivo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1eafc n\u1ecbch ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Ousmane Dembele s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barcelona b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 vi\u1ec7c \u2018bom t\u1ea5n\u2019 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 145 tri\u1ec7u euro n\u00e0y v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i Barca.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao CLB,\u00a0Eric Abidal \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ea5n an ng\u00f4i sao 21 tu\u1ed5i. C\u1ef1u sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Dembele s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Nou Camp \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng Dembele s\u1ebd ra \u0111i sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 23 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, k\u00e9m xa so v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 khi anh c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i\u00a0<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/\" title=\"bong da\" type=\"bong da\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span>\u00a0t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Barca c\u0169ng l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u ch\u1ea5m h\u1ebft cho nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Ousmane Dembele.Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Bartomeu c\u0169ng t\u1eebng\u00a0kh\u0103ng kh\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p cho b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai.\u00a0\"Dembele s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u c\u1ea3. T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 \u1edf Camp Nou.\u00a0C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 Coutinho l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a CLB. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a l\u1edbn lao trong c\u00e1c k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Barca. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng \u1edf h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nOusmane Dembele gia nh\u1eadp Barca \u1edf nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2017 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c. Anh l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 Barca t\u1eebng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n cho t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng chi ph\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 145 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 th\u1ee9 2 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed (sau Neymar). Tuy nhi\u00ean cho t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, CLB Barcelona v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 khai th\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ebft s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/roma-hoi-mua-nzonzi-172-192318.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/17/roma-hoi-mua-nzonzi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/roma-hoi-mua-nzonzi-172-192318.html\">Arsenal v\u00e0 Barca c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 sao tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p</span><br>\r\nRoma mu\u1ed1n mua Steven Nzonzi c\u1ee7a Sevilla, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao c\u1ee7a Monchi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia \u0111\u00e3 bay t\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-xac-nhan-ban-digne-cho-everton-voi-gia-25-trieu-euro-180-192286.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/barca-xac-nhan-ban-digne-cho-everton-voi-gia-25-trieu-euro.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-xac-nhan-ban-digne-cho-everton-voi-gia-25-trieu-euro-180-192286.html\">X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn: Sao Barca c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u euro</span><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Lucas Digne r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 99%, twitter c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1eafp t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<em style=\"outline: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family:\" new=\"\" windowtext=\"\" none=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></em></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1805","checkdouble":"192325"},{"date":"15:38 30/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP PSG vs Atletico Madrid 18h35 ng\u00e0y 30/7 (ICC 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/psg-vs-atletico-madrid-tran-dau-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp PSG vs Atletico Madrid: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u PSG vs Atletico gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu Internationl Champions Cup ICC 2018 l\u00fac 18h35 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 30/7.</h2>(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<h2>TH\u00d4NG TIN</h2>\r\nPSG: H\u1ea7u h\u1ebft tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 World Cup nh\u01b0 Neymar, Mbappe hay Di Maria ch\u01b0a t\u1eadp trung.<br>\r\nAtletico: V\u1eafng Costa, Saul, Koke, Godin, Giminez v\u00e0 Filipe.<br>\r\nTheo ch\u00e2u \u00c1, PSG thua c\u1ea3 8 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Atletico th\u1eafng 6 v\u00e0 thua 2 \u1edf 8 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\nC\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a PSG v\u00e0 5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Atletico \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1 b\u00e0n trong hi\u1ec7p 1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn PSG thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi l\u00e0 b\u1edfi h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o ngo\u00e0i th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Buffon. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Atletico \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i m\u1edbi r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 Lemar, Rodri hay Gelson.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp PSG vs Atletico Madrid tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp PSG vs Atletico Madrid tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/nhan-dinh-psg-vs-atletico-madrid-18h35-ngay-307-icc-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">PSG vs Atletico Madrid</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>PH\u00c1T BI\u1ec2U</h2>\r\nHLV Thomas Tuchel (PSG): \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng. M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u1ed5n h\u01a1n khi c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i\".<br>\r\nHLV Diego Simeone (Atletico): \"Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 PSG tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f2n \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec c\u1ea7n kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c\",<br>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T</h2>\r\nKh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n<br>\r\nC\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a PSG \u0111\u1ec1u k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean. 3/4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Atletico c\u0169ng c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 3 b\u00e0n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng n\u00ean s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Atletico 1-1 (pen 3-1) Arsenal (ICC 2018) </strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/26/Atletico-1-1-Arsenal.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1804","checkdouble":"192326"},{"date":"16:29 30/07","title":"Ibra c\u00f3 hattrick \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/ibra-co-hattrick-dau-tien-tren-dat-my.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ibrahimovic l\u1eadp hattrick si\u00eau \u0111\u1eb3ng gi\u00fap LA Galaxy l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eafng l\u1ea1i 4-3.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nIbra ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">1-0, r\u1ed3i 2-1, Orlando City \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc LA Galaxy khi hi\u1ec7p 1 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i n\u1eeda sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 show di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Zlatan Ibrahimovic. Ph\u00fat 47, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u00f3 pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Dos Santos, g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2 cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. Anh m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa khi\u1ebfn t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng 3-3 sau khi Dom Dwyer gi\u00fap Orlando v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed9c r\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111u\u1ed5i t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u01b0 phim kinh d\u1ecb n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i \u1edf ph\u00fat 71, khi l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 n\u00e0y tung c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1, \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-3 chung cu\u1ed9c cho LA Galaxy. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00fa hattrick \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Ibra tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u anh ghi 3 b\u00e0n trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 26/2/2017 (M.U 3-0 Saint-Etienne).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ibrahimovic l\u1eadp hattrick gi\u00fap LA Galaxy th\u1eafng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf 4-3\" title=\"Ibrahimovic l\u1eadp hattrick\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/ibra-co-hattrick-dau-tien-tren-dat-my.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ibrahimovic l\u1eadp hattrick gi\u00fap LA Galaxy th\u1eafng ngh\u1eb9t&nbsp;th\u1edf 4-3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nV\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch n\u00e0y, ng\u00f4i sao 36 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 15 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 17 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n, tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Anh c\u0169ng gi\u00fap LA Galaxy n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i chu\u1ed7i b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 9, v\u00e0 x\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng b\u1edd \u0110\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a MLS, ch\u1ec9 sau Los Angeles FC v\u00e0 Dallas FC.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Man United, v\u00e0 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng Mourinho h\u00e3y \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c. Tuy nhi\u00ean t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u00edt kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n nh\u01b0 MLS, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y v\u1eabn th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh qua t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ibrahimovic l\u1eadp hattrick l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp th\u00eam s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ec3 anh chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ef1u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Ibra - Wayne Rooney c\u0169ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft DC United (\u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thu\u1ed9c b\u1edd T\u00e2y) v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-dau-tien-cua-rooney-trong-mau-ao-dc-united-331-192328.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/ban-thang-dau-tien-cua-rooney-trong-mau-ao-dc-united.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-dau-tien-cua-rooney-trong-mau-ao-dc-united-331-192328.html\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Rooney trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o DC United</span><br>\r\nSau b\u1ed1n tr\u1eadn thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Audi Field, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ibrahimovic-mu-can-phai-gianh-danh-hieu-mua-nay-172-192149.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/23/ibrahimovic-mu-can-phai-gianh-danh-hieu-mua-nay.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ibrahimovic-mu-can-phai-gianh-danh-hieu-mua-nay-172-192149.html\">Ibrahimovic: MU c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ibrahimovic cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf Man United c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00e0nh \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1803","checkdouble":"192327"}]}